══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  TECH STACK — STRICT, DO NOT DEVIATE
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

FRONTEND
────────
• React 18 + Vite
• Redux Toolkit + RTK Query (all state & API calls)
• React Router v6
• Framer Motion (ALL animations — no CSS-only transitions)
• React Leaflet + Leaflet.js (map engine)
• Leaflet.markercluster (marker clustering)
• Turf.js (geospatial: distance, area, buffer, bbox)
• Socket.io-client (real-time: live location, chat, notifications)
• React Hook Form + Zod (forms & validation)
• Axios (HTTP — only for non-RTK calls)
• Tailwind CSS (utility classes only — no component libraries)

BACKEND
───────
• Node.js + Express.js
• MongoDB + Mongoose (with 2dsphere geospatial indexes)
• Socket.io (real-time engine)
• JWT — access token (15min) + refresh token (7d, httpOnly cookie)
• Passport.js — Local + Google OAuth2 + GitHub OAuth
• bcryptjs (password hashing)
• Multer + Cloudinary (image uploads)
• express-validator (input validation)
• Nominatim API (free geocoding — NO paid API key needed)
• OSRM API (free routing — NO paid API key needed)
• cors, helmet, morgan, dotenv, express-rate-limit

DEV
───
• Monorepo structure: /client (Vite) + /server (Express)
• ESLint + Prettier
• All secrets in .env — never hardcoded

