━━━ 1. AUTHENTICATION ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

• Email & Password (register / login / forgot password)
• Google OAuth2 (one-click login)
• GitHub OAuth (one-click login)
• Guest / Anonymous mode (explore map without account,
  prompt to register when trying to post/save)
• JWT refresh flow — silent token refresh via RTK Query
  baseQuery with re-auth, user never sees session expire
• Protected routes via <PrivateRoute> checking Redux auth state
• Avatar upload on register (Multer + Cloudinary)

Redux auth state shape:
{
  user: { id, name, email, role, avatar, bio, location } | null,
  accessToken: string | null,
  isAuthenticated: boolean,
  isGuest: boolean,
  status: 'idle' | 'loading' | 'succeeded' | 'failed'
}

━━━ 2. MAP — CORE ENGINE ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Map Setup:
• React Leaflet MapContainer — fills entire viewport (position: fixed)
• Tile layer: OpenStreetMap + dark variant toggle
  Light: https://{s}.tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png
  Dark:  https://{s}.basemaps.cartocdn.com/dark_all/{z}/{x}/{y}{r}.png
• Start zoom: 13, min: 3, max: 19
• Custom attribution (minimal, bottom-right)

User Geolocation:
• Auto-request on app load with permission prompt UI
• On success: smooth flyTo() user position, zoom 15, duration 1.5s
• Show animated pulsing dot marker at user position (custom SVG)
• Show accuracy radius circle (semi-transparent blue fill)
• "Locate Me" FAB button — bottom right — re-centers map
• On permission denied: friendly modal with manual search fallback
• Watch position (watchPosition) for real-time tracking when
  live-share is active — updates every 3 seconds

Redux map state shape:
{
  viewport: { center: [lat, lng], zoom: 13 },
  userLocation: { lat, lng, accuracy, heading, timestamp } | null,
  locationError: string | null,
  selectedPin: Pin | null,
  hoveredPinId: string | null,
  mapStyle: 'light' | 'dark' | 'satellite',
  measureMode: false,
  measurePoints: [],
  measureDistance: null,
  activeLayers: ['pins', 'users', 'events'],
  isLocating: boolean
}

━━━ 3. SEARCH & GEOCODING ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

• Floating search bar — top-center of map
• Debounced autocomplete (300ms) via Nominatim:
  GET https://nominatim.openstreetmap.org/search
      ?q={query}&format=json&limit=6&addressdetails=1
• Results in animated glass dropdown (Framer Motion)
• Select result → map.flyTo() with smooth animation
• Reverse geocode on long-press / right-click anywhere on map:
  GET https://nominatim.openstreetmap.org/reverse
      ?lat={lat}&lon={lon}&format=json
• Show address + coordinates in floating info chip
• Server proxies all Nominatim requests (hide from client)
• Recent searches saved to Redux + localStorage

━━━ 4. PINS & LOCATIONS (User-Generated) ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Creating Pins:
• Long-press on map (500ms) → "Create here" context menu appears
• OR: Click "+" FAB → tap location on map
• Pin creation form (bottom sheet on mobile, modal on desktop):
  - Title, description, category (food/nature/art/event/other)
  - Photo upload (up to 5 images via Cloudinary)
  - Visibility: public / friends-only / private
  - Tags (comma-separated)
  - Auto-filled: coordinates + reverse-geocoded address

Custom Markers (NO default Leaflet pins):
• SVG markers colored by category
• User's own pins: filled accent color + user avatar
• Friends' pins: outlined with friend's avatar
• Public pins: subtle gray with category icon
• Hover: scale(1.2) + tooltip with name
• Click: animated bottom sheet / side panel with full details
• Clustering via Leaflet.markercluster for 20+ pins in viewport

Viewing Pins:
• Load only pins within current map viewport:
  GET /api/pins?swLat=&swLng=&neLat=&neLng=&categories=
• Re-fetch on map moveend event (debounced 400ms)
• Pin detail panel shows:
  - Photos carousel
  - Creator avatar + name + follow button
  - Full address + coordinates (click to copy)
  - Distance from user (Turf.js haversine)
  - Reviews list + rating stars
  - "Get Directions" button → draws route

MongoDB Pin Schema:
{
  title: String,
  description: String,
  category: { type: String, enum: ['food','nature','art','event','other'] },
  location: {
    type: { type: String, enum: ['Point'], required: true },
    coordinates: [Number]  // [longitude, latitude] — NOTE: lng FIRST
  },
  address: String,
  images: [String],        // Cloudinary URLs
  createdBy: ObjectId,
  visibility: { type: String, enum: ['public','friends','private'] },
  tags: [String],
  likes: [ObjectId],
  averageRating: Number,
  reviewCount: Number,
  createdAt: Date
}
// CRITICAL: 2dsphere index
pinSchema.index({ location: '2dsphere' });

