━━━ 7. MAP DRAWING TOOLS ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Area Drawing:
• Draw polygon on map (click to add points, double-click to close)
• Drawn area shows fill + border with area in km²  (Turf.js)
