Route / Directions:
• Click any pin → "Get Directions" 
• Draws route via OSRM (free routing):
  GET http://router.project-osrm.org/route/v1/driving/
      {userLng},{userLat};{pinLng},{pinLat}
      ?overview=full&geometries=geojson
• Route drawn as animated dashed polyline on map
• Shows: distance, estimated time, turn-by-turn steps in panel

